<HEADLINE> Greece Signs Contract to Buy French-Made Missiles </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
ATHENS, August 31 (Xinhua) -- Greece Thursday signed a 21-
billion-drachma (about 57 million U.S. dollars) agreement with
France's Aerospatiale Matra company for the purchase of three
artillery fire control systems and 27 guided missiles for the
country's three new naval craft.
</P>
