<HEADLINE> Diplomatic Envoys Visit Gansu Province </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
LANZHOU, August 31 (Xinhua) -- Fifty-nine diplomatic envoys and
their spouses from 38 countries arrived here today, kicking off a
visit to northwest China's Gansu province.
</P>
<P>
Gansu Governor Song Zhaosu briefed the visitors on the province
's plan in developing western China and the problems facing the
local government.
</P>
<P>
