mineral, energy and tourism resources and has achieved great
progress in improving people's living standard.
</P>
<P>
They said that Macao will increase economic and cultural
exchanges with Guizhou and complement each other's good points to
seek common development. They have also put forward many
suggestions with regard to investment, environment protection and
improvement of the culture and education of workers and farmers.
