million HK dollars, or 86.98 percent, more than that of Wednesday.
</P>
<P>
According to Homeway, China's leading on-line financial and
securities company, the market continued Wednesday's downward
trend and failed to revive from its tumble due to lack of investor
's bullish sentiment. At the same time, the turnover was broadly
extended for heavy selling pressure.
</P>
