<HEADLINE> Shanghai B-Share Market Down Thursday </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, August 31 (Xinhua) -- The Shanghai B-share Index
plunged 4.64 points, or 6.55 percent, the largest tumble in a week,
