is expected to be declared next Wednesday, following a meeting
between United States President Bill Clinton and Israeli Prime
Minister Ehud Barak in New York.
</P>
<P>
In addition, the president will announce that he is making a
special aid package available to strengthen the Israel Defense
Forces (IDF).
</P>
<P>
The condition for the upgrade in relations will be an agreement
signed by the two countries to tighten U.S. supervision over
Israeli arms sales.
</P>
