</P>
<P>
-- A misunderstanding between an Israeli junior officer and
soldiers was the apparent cause of the botched operation in which
three soldiers of the elite Duvdevan unit were killed by their
comrades Saturday, according to preliminary military investigations
into the incident.
</P>
<P>
