<P>
Among the men, No. 6 Marat Safin beat Thierry Guardiola 7-5, 6-
7(5), 6-4, 6-4; No. 10 Cedric Pioline beat Sargis Sargsian 6-3, 6-
3,6-1; and No. 15 Philippoussis downed Albert Portas 6-3, 6-2, 6-3.
