Congress Li Peng told United Nations Secretary-General Kofi Annan
Wednesday in New York that the United States' attempt to develop
and deploy the National Missile Defense System will dramatically
change global and regional strategic balance and stability.
</P>
<P>
-- Co-operation and enhanced understanding between China and
the United States is conducive to the further development of Sino-
American relation, State Council Information Minister Zhao Qizheng
said Wednesday while addressing the National Press Club in
Washington. 
</P>
